name: MUTANT-TIGER-006
description:
Family     : Grey
Habitate   : Freezo Tropical Forest, North Area
Attributes : Mask, Leather Coat, Magenta Hair
Activity   : When wear this mask, this tiger oftenly seen on residental areas.

Once upon a time, explorers and researchers found a meteor in a tropical forest. This causes all living things to mutate. Currently, the animal that has been found by explorers and researchers is tiger species.

They have a unique mutation in body shape. And not only that, these animals have revolutionized the way of life. No longer like a tiger who only hunts. They carry out other activities that were previously impossible for these animals.
